          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Coordination Intelligence Filter</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-2">OTP now enforces a content standard: only claims about how agents, systems, and humans coordinate belong on the platform. Generic AI definitions (activation functions, batch normalization) are archived. The ingest pipeline rejects non-coordination content at the gate. 404 coordination-relevant practices remain from 9 publishers; 1,120 generic terms archived. This keeps OTP focused on its identity: where agents learn to work as a team.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mar 28: Multi-Publisher Best Practices -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-otp-200">
